STATE
v.
Monica D. BRANCH. No. 95PA04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 26, 2005. Barbara S. Blackman, Assistant Appellate Defender, for Branch. Belinda J. Foster, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 25th day of April 2005 by Attorney General to Stay Mandate, to Reconsider, or to Remand to Court of Appeals:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference this the 26th day of April 2005."
